{"id":"ced862d2-1859-44e4-a503-c71c2d31f03d","name":"RUNRUNRUN| KENJI","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">The boyfriend distribution system choose you!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Congrats you got yourself a biker boyfriend, you bump into his bike and make a run for it, and now? Pay for your consequences.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">────୨ৎ────</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 96, 96)\"><strong>#DAZEDRIFT|#BIKER|#FUNNY|#FLIRTY</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">“You left a mess behind. Hit and run—thought you could just vanish?”</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">────୨ৎ────</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 96, 96)\"><strong>#BIKER!CHAR X ANY!USER</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(211, 107, 169); color: inherit\">𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐱𝐭 ── ✦</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You stomped on the boots of the wrong biker!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Or maybe the right one?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Mix trauma, drama and zero awareness of personal space and you get Kenji Inaba.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(211, 107, 169); color: inherit\">♡𝐚𝐛𝐨𝐮𝐭 𝐮𝐬𝐞𝐫♡</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Hey, little angel! This time I sent you an agent of chaos, you might have been a bit clumsy and scratched his bite a <em>little</em> or a <em>lot</em>, your choice, but either way you gotta pay!</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">OTHER Daze Drift bots:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a9a91ecf-639b-4bb3-a2cb-5c5728ec0e6b_character-the-biker-callahan-reeves\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">The Biker - Callahan Reeves</a> by <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/e2f491aa-f0